---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const SITE = 'https://andybanguiau.github.io/netandip-site';
---
<Layout
  title="Télécharger NetAndIP — Gestionnaire d'adresses IP Windows"
  description="Téléchargez NetAndIP gratuitement. Gestionnaire de configuration réseau pour Windows 10 et 11. Sans inscription, sans données collectées."
  canonical={`${SITE}/download`}
>
  <main>
    <section class="dl-page">
      <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
        <header class="section-header center">
          <span class="section-label">Téléchargement</span>
          <h1 class="section-title">Télécharger NetAndIP</h1>
          <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0 auto;">Version 3.0.0 — Windows 10 / 11 x64 — Gratuit, sans inscription</p>
        </header>

        <div class="dl-grid">
          <div class="dl-card primary">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;">
              <h3>Installateur Windows</h3>
              <span class="tag-badge">Recommandé</span>
            </div>
            <p>Installe NetAndIP avec raccourci bureau et programme de désinstallation.</p>
            <div class="dl-meta-row">
              <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>NetAndIP-Setup-3.0.0-x64.exe — ~23 Mo</span>
              <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/></svg>Windows 10 / 11 — x64</span>
            </div>
            <a href="https://github.com/AndyBanguiau/netandip/releases/latest/download/NetAndIP-Setup-3.0.0-x64.exe" class="btn btn-primary" rel="noopener" data-download="download-page-installer" style="justify-content:center;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
              Télécharger l'installateur
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="dl-card">
            <h3>Version portable</h3>
            <p>Exécutable unique, aucune installation. Idéal pour clé USB ou environnements restreints.</p>
            <div class="dl-meta-row">
              <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>NetAndIP.exe — ~21 Mo</span>
              <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/></svg>Windows 10 / 11 — x64</span>
            </div>
            <a href="https://github.com/AndyBanguiau/netandip/releases/latest/download/NetAndIP.exe" class="btn btn-ghost" rel="noopener" data-download="download-page-portable" style="justify-content:center;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
              Télécharger le .exe portable
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="dl-smartscreen" role="note" aria-label="Information Windows SmartScreen">
          <div class="dl-smartscreen-icon">⚠</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Windows SmartScreen peut afficher un avertissement</h4>
            <p>C'est normal pour un logiciel indépendant distribué sans certificat coûteux. Le code source est ouvert sur GitHub.</p>
            <ol>
              <li>Cliquez sur <strong>« Informations complémentaires »</strong></li>
              <li>Cliquez sur <strong>« Exécuter quand même »</strong></li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="dl-req">
          <h3>Configuration requise</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Windows 10 (64-bit) ou Windows 11</li>
            <li>Droits administrateur pour appliquer une configuration réseau</li>
            <li>~50 Mo d'espace disque</li>
            <li>Connexion internet uniquement pour les mises à jour (désactivable)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align:center;font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text-3);margin-top:2rem;">
          Problème avec le téléchargement ?
          <a href="mailto:banguiauandy@gmail.com" style="color:var(--primary);">Contactez le support</a>
          ou consultez les
          <a href="https://github.com/AndyBanguiau/netandip/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--primary);">releases GitHub</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .dl-page { padding: 8rem 0 5rem; min-height: 70vh; }
  .dl-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
  .dl-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .dl-card.primary { border-color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--primary), 0 8px 32px rgba(99,102,241,.15); }
  .dl-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--fg); margin: 0; }
  .dl-card p { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--fg-muted); margin: 0; }
  .dl-meta-row { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .4rem; }
  .dl-meta-row span { font-size: .8rem; color: var(--fg-muted); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .4rem; }
  .dl-req { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .dl-req h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  .dl-req ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .4rem; list-style: disc; }
  .dl-req li { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--fg-muted); }
  .dl-smartscreen { background: rgba(251,191,36,.06); border: 1px solid rgba(251,191,36,.2); border-radius: .75rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem; }
  .dl-smartscreen-icon { font-size: 1.25rem; flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 1.4; }
  .dl-smartscreen h4 { font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 600; color: #fbbf24; margin: 0 0 .3rem; }
  .dl-smartscreen p { font-size: .85rem; color: var(--fg-muted); margin: 0; }
  .dl-smartscreen ol { font-size: .85rem; color: var(--fg-muted); margin: .5rem 0 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
  .dl-smartscreen li { margin-bottom: .15rem; }
  .tag-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .3rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,.12); color: var(--primary); border-radius: .25rem; font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 600; padding: .2rem .5rem; letter-spacing: .04em; }
  @media (max-width: 640px) { .dl-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
